description:
This one might go down as one of my favorite Serviced videos.
Jayce was really turned on by the whole process, and sometimes I feel like the guys are too nervous to enjoy themselves. Jayce let go and just went for it.
And to have a chance to eat his ass out...wow! He's got ass for days! He even let me finger him which brought him even closer. He grinds down on it like he wants more.
Its a longer than normal 'Serviced' video, but it went so well that so many moments were enjoyable, it was hard to get it down to a more downloadable size.
Hope you enjoy this one, I know I did!
title: Bryan & Jayce - Serviced
